org.apache.drill.jdbc

Class ResultSetGetMethodConversionsTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.drill.test.BaseTest
      • org.apache.drill.test.DrillTest
        • org.apache.drill.exec.ExecTest
          • org.apache.drill.jdbc.JdbcTestBase
            • org.apache.drill.jdbc.ResultSetGetMethodConversionsTest

  • public class ResultSetGetMethodConversionsTest
extends JdbcTestBase
    Integration-level unit test for ResultSet's getType(column ID) methods' type conversions.

    This test class is intended for higher-level type-vs.-type coverage tests. Detailed-case tests (e.g., boundary conditions) are intended to be in TypeConvertingSqlAccessor).
